 Novara, Piedmont, Italy","lifeSummary":"When Ubertus Pirovano was born in 1198, in Invorio, Novara, Piedmont, Italy, his father, Archbishop Uberto  Provano, was 26 and his mother, Mrs Uberto Pirovano, was 23. He married Countess Casati in 1223, in Invorio Inferiore, Novara, Piedmont, Italy. They were the parents of at least 1 daughter. He died in 1226, in his hometown, at the age of 28, and was buried in Invorio, Novara, Piedmont, Italy."},"et":{"1198–1226":"1198–1226","1203–1247":"1203–1247","1226–1276":"1226–1276","1172–1278":"1172–1278","1175–1245":"1175–1245","1226":"1226","1247":"1247","1203":"1203","1223":"1223","1245":"1245","1278":"1278","1276":"1276","1198":"1198","1175":"1175","1172":"1172","Invorio, Novara, Piemonte, Itália":"Invorio, Novara, Piemonte, Itaalia","Invorio Inferiore, Novara, Piemonte, Itália":"Invorio Inferiore, Novara, Piemonte, Itaalia","Invorio, Piemonte IT":"Invorio, Novara, Piemonte, Itaalia","Invorio Inferiore, Invorio, Novara, Piedmont, Italy":"Invorio Inferiore, Novara, Piemonte, Itaalia"},"fi":{"1198–1226":"1198–1226","1203–1247":"1203–1247","1226–1276":"1226–1276","1172–1278":"1172–1278","1175–1245":"1175–1245","1226":"1226","1247":"1247","1203":"1203","1223":"1223","1245":"1245","1278":"1278","1276":"1276","1198":"1198","1175":"1175","1172":"1172","Invorio, Novara, Piemonte, Itália":"Invorio, Novara, Piemonte, Italia","Invorio Inferiore, Novara, Piemonte, Itália":"Invorio Inferiore, Novara, Piemonte, Italia","Invorio, Piemonte IT":"Invorio, Novara, Piemonte, Italia","Invorio Inferiore, Invorio, Novara, Piedmont, Italy":"Invorio Inferiore, Novara, Piemonte, Italia"},"fr":{"1198–1226":"1198–1226","1203–1247":"1203–1247","1226–1276":"1226–1276","1172–1278":"1172–1278","1175–1245":"1175–1245","1226":"1226","1247":"1247","1203":"1203","1223":"1223","1245":"1245","1278":"1278","1276":"1276","1198":"1198","1175":"1175","1172":"1172","Invorio, Novara, Piemonte, Itália":"Invorio, Novara, Piemonte, Italie","Invorio Inferiore, Novara, Piemo